The obtained exosome precipitate is suspended in 14 μl 0.3% SDS solution, 5 μl acrylamide solution (30%), 0.7 μl of 1% ammonium persulfate, and 0.3 μl of TEMED are mixed and polymerized at room temperature for about 30 minutes. The small gel is cut into 1 mm 
